{
  "text": "At the end of this first 25, 000-year cycle, then, was there any physical change that occurred rapidly like that which occurs at a 75, 000-year cycle or is this just an indexing time for a harvesting period? I am Ra. There was no change except that which according to intelligent energy, or what you may term physical evolution, suited physical complexes to their environment, this being of the color of the skin due to the area of the sphere upon which entities lived; the gradual growth of peoples due to improved intake of foodstuffs.",
